# Backend API URL — set this to your Render deployment URL in production.
# In local development this is NOT needed; the Vite dev-server proxy handles /api → localhost:5000.
#
# For Vercel deployment, add this as an Environment Variable in the Vercel project dashboard,
# or create a .env.production file (gitignored) locally for production preview builds.
VITE_API_URL=https://your-render-service-name.onrender.com
